//Pericardium

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 09 of Cardio MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Pericardium' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Pericardial effusion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Calcification' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Pericardial effusion' checkbox
Then 'Max width' input field is enabled

When I select 'Calcification' checkbox
Then 'Constrictive pericarditis' checkbox is enabled
